{"tid":595263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於的士罷駛，朋友傳來的真實不幸事件","createTime":"2018-03-16T13:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T15:47:21.000Z","uid":100150,"like":154,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"60a7b9829b6dda4954db5eb4ed958dd4cef64b7a","tid":595263,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"朋友傳來的真實不幸事件...<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......反對 UBER 白牌車我是十分支持，只不過不要把你們的行動影響別人的生活。剛剛我wts app一個朋友恭喜他妻子生了女兒，但是他給我只是一個黑暗的回復，他說他老婆今天下午只有她一個人，因作動而叫救護車，但救護車未能夠準時到達接他老婆，然後traffic jam 45分鐘才到律敦治醫院。醫生告訴他們 你們女兒嚴重腦缺氧，大量腦細胞死亡，可能日後會有點問題。有點問題即係傻？我只可以打一個長途電話安慰他。希望 的哥們放棄你的自私，遊行你們可否到其他地方？......&quot;理性啲啦！"},{"pid":"0d83b4c3c2a672d6181198e75ed2b7ef4f700956","tid":595263,"uid":33439,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:17:44.000Z","msg":"最衰佔中 搞到的士佬冇生意去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604ce90a556bc4dd3a6b00ac9488e4de0feaa6f5","tid":595263,"uid":100150,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"0d83b4c3c2a672d6181198e75ed2b7ef4f700956","tid":595263,"uid":33439,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:17:44.000Z","msg":"最衰佔中 搞到的士佬冇生意去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得佔中班的士佬好唔理性囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爭取權利可以和平解決，阻到人就唔啱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b608ce9cd6ddc110ceba12b5beff0591945d7822","tid":595263,"uid":63311,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"的士廢老搞搞陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6527204af763723d69d52abb3d78cb92113ebb","tid":595263,"uid":100150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b608ce9cd6ddc110ceba12b5beff0